00:03.600 --> 00:06.200
      <i>Last time on</i> Cheers:      

00:06.200 --> 00:08.600
     Hey, Sam, me and Eddie     
      are getting married!      

00:08.600 --> 00:10.500
 She's, uh, quite a catch, Ed.  

00:10.600 --> 00:13.100
