the one day of the century      

00:13.100 --> 00:15.100
when all the planets            
and constellations              

00:15.100 --> 00:16.400
are in perfect alignment.       

00:16.500 --> 00:19.300
    So we either get married    
      by 4:00 p.m. today,       

00:19.400 --> 00:21.000
or we wait until the year 2042. 

00:21.100 --> 00:22.700
      This is going to be       
    an interesting wedding,     

00:22.800 --> 00:24.800
the two most superstitious      
      people in the world.      

00:24.800 --> 00:26.700
Hey, hey, don't say that.       
It's bad luck.                  

00:26.800 --> 00:29.900
            Our love can conquer
            any bad luck        
            that comes our way. 

