01:25.500 --> 01:27.300
                the wedding's   
                been called off.

01:27.400 --> 01:29.500
             Ah...              

01:29.500 --> 01:30.900
    So what happened?           

01:31.000 --> 01:32.700
    Eddie freaked out           
     about being a father?      

01:32.700 --> 01:33.700
No.                             

01:33.700 --> 01:36.100
     Eddie's mom met Carla.     

01:36.100 --> 01:36.900
      Hate at first sight.      

01:36.900 --> 01:38.100
     Yeah, how'd you know?      

01:38.200 --> 01:40.900
  Well, that's the "law" part   
    of "mother-in-law," see.    

01:40.900 --> 01:42.700
So Eddie's not going            
to marry Carla                  

01:42.800 --> 01:44.800
because his mother              
doesn't approve.                

01:44.800 --> 01:46.000
I tell you,                     
it's pathetic                   

01:46.000 --> 01:50.500
to see a grown man so tied      
to his ma's apron strings.      

01:50.500 --> 01:52.800
     Well, that reminds me,     
 Mr. Clavin, you mother called  

01:52.800 --> 01:55.200
