08:43.700 --> 08:45.500
        Ah, I can't talk        
        to him now, man.        

08:45.600 --> 08:47.400
 I-I gotta talk to Eddie here.  

08:47.500 --> 08:48.800
    I just talked to Eddie.     

08:48.800 --> 08:50.200
     I gotta talk to Carla.     

08:50.200 --> 08:51.300
Carla?                          
                    Mm-hmm.     

08:51.300 --> 08:52.300
        Carla.                  

08:54.000 --> 08:55.800
         Father Berry?          

08:55.900 --> 08:58.400
     Listen, Sam can't talk     
     right now, but, uh...      

08:58.500 --> 09:02.700
 while I got you on the phone,  
can I ask you a question?       

09:02.700 --> 09:05.000
      Do you have to pay        
      any membership dues       

09:05.100 --> 09:07.600
    to be a Catholic?           

09:07.600 --> 09:10.400
                     I told you 
                     I wouldn't 
                     talk to him

09:10.400 --> 09:12.600
                unless he comes 
                in here begging.

09:12.600 --> 09:15.400
    Come on. Carla, we don't    
  have time for this nonsense.  

09:16.700 --> 09:17.800
Hey, I got an idea.             

09:17.800 --> 09:19.600
Get out of your clothes.        

09:19.600 --> 09:22.900
        Oh, Sammy,              
  any other time I'd love to,   

09:22.900 --> 09:24.100
         but, really...         

09:24.200 --> 09:26.200
    Well, I just think that,    
  you know, uh, you're sweaty.  

09:26.300 --> 09:27.500
You're tired,                   
Maybe you'd                     

09:27.600 --> 09:29.700
         like to change         
      into something else.      

09:29.800 --> 09:31.800
Well, hey, like this,           
for instance.                   

09:31.800 --> 09:32.900
            No way.             

09:33.000 --> 09:34.900
          Oh, come on.          
     Just, just try it on.      

09:35.000 --> 09:36.000
You know, see how it fits       

09:36.000 --> 09:37.800
        in case you want        
    to get married someday.     

09:38.500 --> 09:39.600
        Years from now.         

09:39.600 --> 09:40.700
Years from now.                 
        Well, you know,         

09:40.800 --> 09:41.800
 I might not be pregnant then.  

09:41.800 --> 09:43.000
             Right.             

09:45.500 --> 09:46.200
    Come on.                    

09:46.300 --> 09:47.400
              Oh, what the heck.

09:47.400 --> 09:49.300
            This might be the   
            last chance I get   

09:49.400 --> 09:51.600
        to see what I look      
        like in one of these.   

09:51.600 --> 09:52.700
    Yeah.                       

09:52.800 --> 09:54.200
    Besides, I'm out 36 bucks.  

09:57.700 --> 09:59.400
         Eddie, Eddie.          

09:59.400 --> 10:00.500
                          Sammy.

10:00.500 --> 10:02.700
 I know what you're doing here. 

10:02.800 --> 10:05.200
        You think I'm going     
        to get all decked out   

10:05.300 --> 10:07.000
                 like Miss Bride
                 of the Year,   

10:07.000 --> 10:08.500
                take one look   
                in the mirror   

10:08.500 --> 10:10.800
            and forget all about
            being mad at Eddie. 

10:10.800 --> 10:12.300
                and I'm going   
                to go out there,

10:12.300 --> 10:14.400
            and Eddie's going to
            take one look at me 

10:14.500 --> 10:17.000
            and forget all about
            his mother. <i>Then,</i>   

10:17.100 --> 10:20.100
    we'll march down the aisle  
    and live happily ever after.

10:20.100 --> 10:23.000
                     Am I right?

10:23.000 --> 10:24.100
Yeah, that's basically it.      

10:24.200 --> 10:25.500
  You got a problem with that?  

