Ah, look at you.                

10:49.200 --> 10:50.100
( <i>laughing</i> )                    

10:50.200 --> 10:52.000
                 Okay. Let's    
                 give it a shot.

10:52.000 --> 10:53.500
    All right.                  

10:53.500 --> 10:55.200
    Sammy, zip me.              

10:55.200 --> 10:56.400
        Well, I'll be darned.   

10:56.500 --> 10:58.200
                 These things go
                 up, too, huh?  

